node.text:
Ready to sweat? Pilates blew my mind! Join me & Vic moving in a new way with Pilates!
.
You can visit her page her ➡️ @victoriapopoff 
.
She’s giving us a FREE month of virtual workouts with her if you use the code “JESSICA” at www.studioVtv.com
.
My outfit is from my upcoming athletic clothing line!! 😍 Can’t wait to share it with you!
.
Who wants more Pilates in their life? When would you go live with us to workout?
.
.
#virtualpilates
#studiovtv
#pilatesforanyone

node.text:
This is 36! 🤍 🥳

My birthday was 8.27.85. Feeling so incredibly blessed with another year to learn and grow as a woman. I was surrounded by my favorite people in my life MY FAMILY & FRIENDS! (Stay tuned for bday spam).

Thank you to everyone that spent this special day with me it truly,truly meant the world that y’all made it! Cheers to another year of HEALTH & HAPPINESS!

Also thank YOU for all the birthday messages, texts, DMS, etc. I truly felt special this year!❤️
